ds) accommodation with\r\nbreakfast at a 3-star category hotel in Kathmandu &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;The best available twin sharing lodge to lodge\r\naccommodation during the trek, we provide you attached bathroom with ha ot\r\nshower at Lukla, Phakding, and Namche.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Guide&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;1 professional, English Speaking and certified guide for\r\nthe group.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;1 Sharing porter between two hikers i.e. 1 porter\r\nbetween 2 hikers.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Meals&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Buffet Breakfast at a hotel in Kathmandu.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;