/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Comprehensive first aid medical kit including an Oximeter\r\nto measure your Oxygen and Pulse in high altitude carried by the guide during\r\nthe trek. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;All required trekking permits.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Government taxes and office service charge&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Transport&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;,sans-serif&quot;&gt;Airport pickup and drop off by private vehicle.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'uploads/package_24', 1, '2023-08-23 02:37:59');

